{"tid":1714104,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"各位手足，千其唔好輕敵","createTime":"2019-11-12T23:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T23:43:29.000Z","uid":81657,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ffc8ba0d24efeca6a0318a7bec77de3ba8b614cc","tid":1714104,"uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:42:25.000Z","msg":"而家全香港一半癱瘓，証明和理勇武合作效果一定超出預期。中共睇到咁嘅情況，一定叫傀儡林鄭控制警狗提升武力，將真正香港人置諸死地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋晚，咁多區嘅手足出嚟對抗，圍壁救趙，將狗力無得集中暴大，令學生可以睇到今日黎明，多謝各位手足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊將呢份堅持同信念延續落去，証明俾全世界睇，我哋真正嘅香港人寧為玉碎，不為瓦全。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bacaea5eb1f71ad53016de8a998e82dca08bef","tid":1714104,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:43:29.000Z","msg":"宜家班差佬休息緊<br />\n各區手足又好難互相支援<br />\n有咩可以搞？冇理由比對面回氣"}]}